dia thatThe Last Supperdisplay was not meant to be offensive and defended the vision of the ceremony's artistic director Thomas Jolly.\", \"from\": 2518, \"to\": 2728, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2573, \"end\": 2581, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}, {\"begin\": 2715, \"end\": 2721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"score\": 0.6946458385520131, \"rank\": 0.43958250073294197, \"text\": \"Thomas\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Thomas_the_Apostle\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sunday\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"a spokesperson\", \"from\": 2529, \"to\": 2543}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2566}, {\"ngram\": \"the media\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"Last Supperdisplay\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2624}, {\"ngram\": \"the vision\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony's artistic director\", \"from\": 2682, \"to\": 2714}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Clearly there was never an intention to show disrespect to any religious group,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 2730, \"to\": 2821, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an intention\", \"from\": 2755, \"to\": 2767}, {\"ngram\": \"any religious group\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"On the contrary, I think (with) Thomas Jolly, we really did try to celebrate community tolerance,\\\" Descamps said.\", \"from\": 2822, \"to\": 2936, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2922, \"end\": 2930, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Descamps\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jean-Baptiste_Descamps\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the contrary\", \"from\": 2826, \"to\": 2838}, {\"ngram\": \"community tolerance\", \"from\": 2900, \"to\": 2919}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Looking at the result of the polls that we shared, we believe that this ambition was achieved.\", \"from\": 2937, \"to\": 3032, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 2949, \"to\": 2959}, {\"ngram\": \"the polls\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 2972}, {\"ngram\": \"this ambition\", \"from\": 3005, \"to\": 3018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If people have taken any offense we are, of course, really, really sorry.\\\"\", \"from\": 3033, \"to\": 3107, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3042}, {\"ngram\": \"any offense\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3065}, {\"ngram\": \"course\", \"from\": 3077, \"to\": 3083}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Jolly toldThe Associated Pressafter the ceremony, \\\"My wish is not to be subversive, nor to mock or to shock.\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3217, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Jolly toldThe Associated Pressafter\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3144}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3157}, {\"ngram\": \"My wish\", \"from\": 3160, \"to\": 3167}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most of all, I wanted to send a message of love, a message of inclusion and not at all to divide.\\\"\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3316, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3257}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 3261, \"to\": 3265}, {\"ngram\": \"a message\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3276}, {\"ngram\": \"inclusion\", \"from\": 3280, \"to\": 3289}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you have a storyNewsweekshould be covering?\", \"from\": 3318, \"to\": 3364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Do you have any questi